definitions.definition: A vein in the wing of an insect .
Any of the veins that form the branching framework of conducting and supporting tissues in a leaf or other plant organ.
One of the ribs in a groined vault ; a projecting moulding.

main_definition: ( zoology ) A vein in the wing of an insect .
secondary_definitions: ( botany , now rare ) Any of the veins that form the branching framework of conducting and supporting tissues in a leaf or other plant organ.
( architecture ) One of the ribs in a groined vault ; a projecting moulding.
